content.$t: reviews: TADA is is one of those small urban miracles you hope for and rarely see. The miracle maker is owner Kara Jacobson, the wonder is a dance studio of beauty and superb technical construction tucked neatly and conveniently in Cheshire Square. For anyone whose interest is jazz, hip-hop, tap, ballet or contemporary, beginner to advanced, The Atlanta Dance Academy has no equal. On top of that, the teaching​ staff has great breadth and experience., stitle: Birthday Parties, sphoto: birthday.PNG, salt: Kids birthday party, stext: We specialize in ballerina birthdays, hip-hop dance parties, Sweet 16 parties and more., slink: /about
